note right of reservation501
The implementation completes the Reservation immediately
when checkOut() is called.
Table release is handled later by TableReleaseJob
after bufferMinutes have elapsed.
end note

note bottom of table08
At this exact snapshot the dining session has ended,
but the table can still remain OCCUPIED until the
buffer release scheduler marks it AVAILABLE.
end note

